# 2. Leaders in Array

### Problem

An element is a leader if all elements to its right are smaller.

Example

```
16 17 4 3 5 2
```

Output

```
17 5 2
```

### Brute Force

For every element

Compare with every element on right.

Time

```
O(n²)
```

### Optimal

Traverse from right.

Keep maximum seen so far.

If current > maximum

Leader.

Time

```
O(n)
```

Space

```
O(1)
```

### Industry Example

Highest response time remaining in a stream of monitoring data.

